  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to compare tissue quality and molecular yield between a novel&#xD;
      crown-cut biopsy needle (FNB) and a standard aspiration needle (FNA) for EUS-guided diagnosis&#xD;
      of solid pancreatic lesions.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
